### Processing Pipeline (tasks.py)
1. process_event() — orchestrator, dispatches chord of per-photo tasks
2. process_single_photo() — image_pipeline (pyvips→Pillow), InsightFace, 
   returns serialized embeddings
3. finalize_event() — chord callback: bulk DB writes, DBSCAN clustering via 
   FAISS IndexFlatIP, merge pass (MERGE_THRESHOLD=0.82), FAISS search index 
   rebuild, triggers AI enrichment
4. enrich_event_photos() → ai_enrich_event() — Places365 + YOLOv8n, 
   batched commits (ENRICH_BATCH_SIZE=25)
5. cleanup_expired_events() — Celery Beat daily 03:00 UTC

### Search Architecture
- FaissManager: in-process cache with mtime-based invalidation (solves 
  cross-process staleness between FastAPI and Celery worker)
- search_service.py: multi-embedding search (original + 3 augments: flip, 
  center crop, brightness boost), best-score-per-image deduplication
- Thresholds: STRICT=0.68, NORMAL=0.55, FALLBACK=0.40, MAX_RESULTS=1000
- Public search caches results in-memory (CACHE_TTL=30min, PAGE_SIZE=30)

