- Free tier: 50 photos, 10 guest slots, 7 days (one per user account)
- All values DB-configurable via admin panel → PUT /pricing/config

### Key Design Decisions
- Guest photos require owner approval before processing; guest_uploads_used 
  incremented only on approval, not on upload
- PIN stored as salt:sha256_hash, brute-forced 0000-9999 to recover plain 
  PIN for owner display (10K iterations, ~10ms)
- FAISS indexes always on local disk; photos/thumbnails in object storage
- Celery chord: all per-photo tasks must complete before finalize_event runs
- Redis keys for processing progress have 24h TTL; phase key kept 1h after 
  completion for frontend polling
- Watermark applied client-side via Canvas API; config stored per-event in DB
- Admin panel at /admin requires role=admin in JWT; protected by admin 
  layout redirect

